  "text": "In the first phase of our strategy we map each instruction ι ∈ I f to a vector of real numbers ι, using the word2vec model [CITATION_1] . Word2vec is an extremely popular feature learning technique in natural language processing. We use a large corpus of instructions to train our instruction embedding model (see Section 5.1), we call our mapping instruction2vec (i2v). The final outcome of this step is a sequence of vectors I f .",
